<h3>Running the dev environment</h3>

<p>Once you have the Ember project setup, you can start the dev environment by running <code>ember server</code> in your command line. After that, navigate to <a href="http://localhost:4200/" target="_blank">http://localhost:4200</a> to see the game in action.</p>
